import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <header>
      <Container>
        <Row>
          <Col>
            欢迎光临！！
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>

    </header>
  )
}

export default Header
